Router

DELETE /boards/:id

  • rejects unauthorized users

    DEL
    DELETE 
    /boards/53d342c88627c54ead133abd
    Sample request
    headers payload curl 
    /boards/53d342c88627c54ead133abd
    content-type: application/json
x-auth-token: ---
content-length: 19

    {
  "name": "my board"
}
    curl -X DELETE -H "content-type: application/json" -H "x-auth-token: ---" -H "content-length: 19" -d '{"name":"my board"}' "http://my-api.com/boards/53d342c88627c54ead133abd"
    Response 401 Unauthorized
    body 
    "Unauthorized"

  • deletes the board

    GET
    GET 
    /boards/53d342c88627c54ead133ac3
    Sample request
    headers payload curl 
    /boards/53d342c88627c54ead133ac3
    content-type: application/json
x-auth-token: userToken
content-length: 19

    {
  "name": "my board"
}
    curl -X GET -H "content-type: application/json" -H "x-auth-token: userToken" -H "content-length: 19" -d '{"name":"my board"}' "http://my-api.com/boards/53d342c88627c54ead133ac3"

    body 
    "Not Found"

  • returns authorized boards

GET /session

  • rejects unauthorized users

    GET
    GET 
    /session
    Sample request
    curl 
    /session
    curl -X GET "http://my-api.com/session"
    Response 401 Unauthorized
    body 
    "Unauthorized"

  • returns the user's session

    GET
    GET 
    /session
    Sample request
    headers curl 
    /session
    x-auth-token: userToken

    curl -X GET -H "x-auth-token: userToken" "http://my-api.com/session"
    Response 200 OK
    headers body 
    content-type: application/json; charset=utf-8

    {
  "_id": "53d342c08627c54ead1339bd",
  "uid": "theusername",
  "hash": "$2a$10$e9mTnwjfT8sBSlDJDy2yoONrX52MKtDqeGN9lHpEhr04TlQqaU7X6",
  "token": "userToken",
  "session": {
    "misc": "data"
  },
  "__v": 0
}

POST /boards

  • rejects unauthorized users

    POST
    POST 
    /boards
    Sample request
    curl 
    /boards
    curl -X POST "http://my-api.com/boards"
    Response 401 Unauthorized
    body 
    "Unauthorized"

  • returns the board id

    POST
    POST 
    /boards
    Sample request
    headers payload curl 
    /boards
    content-type: application/json
x-auth-token: userToken
content-length: 19

    {
  "name": "my board"
}
    curl -X POST -H "content-type: application/json" -H "x-auth-token: userToken" -H "content-length: 19" -d '{"name":"my board"}' "http://my-api.com/boards"
    Response 201 Created
    body 
    {
  "board": {
    "_id": "53d342c38627c54ead1339c4"
  }
}

    Sample request
    headers payload curl 
    /boards/53d342cd8627c54ead133b22/github/1234/webhook
    content-type: application/json
x-auth-token: userToken
content-length: 98

    {
  "name": "my board",
  "openIssues": [
    {

    Response 204 No Content
